cu.explanation_en: Setting Asn1_verbosity to an invalid enum value 'invalid' will cause ASN.1 verbosity configuration parsing failure.

du.explanation_en: Setting dl_carrierBandwidth to 200 exceeds the valid range (typically up to 106 for certain bands) and will cause downlink carrier bandwidth configuration errors leading to frequency allocation failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將 dl_carrierBandwidth 設定為 200 超過有效範圍（通常對於某些頻帶最多為 106），會導致下行鏈路載波頻寬配置錯誤並造成頻率分配失敗。
